reviews.review_text: Maine Ten Excellent quality! Love these matrix boards! Phil and Jerry trade some great licks during Playin', Phil pretty spirited whole night. Much liquid this weekend....saw every Maine show from 82 Cumberland Civic thru to these babies! Great showing for 88; plus Little Feat and the little airplane dude Sunday night.....and cheap lobsters!
